Microsoft Internship
10 Oct
... a project looking at how technology can
better support high-density and high-rise
residential communities. The tools available
to tenants are currently quite limited in spite
of the many challenges and problems that come
from high-rise living. This project will design, test
and evaluate solutions to meet the specific
needs of these communities.
READ THE FULL PROPOSAL
An exciting opportunity for a 3-month internship at Microsoft, Cambridge. It starts in

encourage any PhD student with an interest in our porject to send us their cv and
something about why they like what they see and what they could bring to the project!
